  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: A user may expect that Transaction Details screen will update itself automatically when needed (it was also my expectation). But, it does not. The only way to refresh it is to go back and open the screen again. It's not very intuitive.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/41651794-b0ec84f8-7481-11e8-9a7c-2e052daafc38.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTransaction Details screen refreshes itself automatically.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe only way to refesh Transaction Details screen is to close and open it again.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Send a transaction\r\n- Go to Transaction History and open the transaction details\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.20\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
